public class LinuxLocalUserImpl
extends UserImpl
implements LinuxLocalUser

An implementation of the model object 'Linux Local User'.

The following features are implemented:

  • Account Description
  • Account Disabled
  • Change Password Next Logon
  • Full Name
  • Home Dir
  • Password Never Expires
  • Shell
  • User Cannot Change Password
  • User Name
